high_descs: Turn to the left and then turn right. Face the white table on the left side.
Pick up the pencil from the left side of the white table.
Carry the pencil and turn to the left then face the wall on the right.
Open the right side drawer and place the pencil inside. Shut the drawer.
Turn around to the right and face the white table.
Pick up the pencil from the white table.
Hold the pencil and turn and face the wall on the left.
Open the right drawer and place the pencil inside.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils to a drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the bed then turn left and cross the room, turn left to face the side of the white desk
Pick up the leftmost pencil that is sitting on the white desk
Turn left and walk to the end of the bed, then turn right and face the drawers that are built into the wall
Open the bottom right hand drawer and place the pencil inside and shut the drawer
Head across the room to the built in drawers then turn right to face the white desk
Pick up the yellow pencil sitting on the desk
Turn around and take a step forward then turn left and and walk past the desk chair, turn around to face the drawers built into the wall
Open the bottom right drawer and place the pencil inside then close the drawer
Turn left and right side of the desk.
Pick up the pencil closest to the chair at the desk.
Go across the room to the drawers with the phone on top.
Put the pencil in the second drawer on the right.
Turn right to the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Turn back to the drawers on the left.
Put the pencil in the second drawer on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils in the drawer.
